<paragraph blockId="3.[160,1155,1346,1441]" pageId="3" pageNumber="684">
This species is currently known only from Santa Terezinha 
<emphasis box="[814,827,1382,1406]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="684">–</emphasis>
<collectingRegion box="[834,983,1382,1406]" country="Brazil" name="Paraiba" pageId="3" pageNumber="684">Paraíba State</collectingRegion>
, and Serrinha 
<emphasis box="[1142,1155,1382,1406]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="684">–</emphasis>
<collectingRegion box="[160,290,1417,1441]" country="Brazil" name="Bahia" pageId="3" pageNumber="684">Bahia State</collectingRegion>
, two localities in the semiarid region of north-eastern 
<collectingCountry box="[913,976,1417,1441]" name="Brazil" pageId="3" pageNumber="684">Brazil</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
